(58, 58, NULL, 3, 'Smartsearch Plugins Work', 'This pull request does a number of things.\r<br>1. It fixes the line endings in the smartsearch/finder plugins\r<br>2. It updates the queries to use the 2.5 version of the database including new fields and field name changes (such as meta data, created_by etc).\r<br>3. It adds position taxa to contacts.\r<br>4. It adds language taxa to all content types (allowing filters based on language, which is a first step to more fully incorporating multlingual content into smart search).\r<br>5. Since all core content must be in categories removes the condition for creation of category taxa. ', 3, 0, 10, '2011-12-23 08:20:14', '2011-12-23 13:45:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/58.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
