(247, 247, NULL, 3, ' use the correct json content-type header when sending json data ', 'Shouldn''t this be fixed at a lower level?<br><br>Anyway, a fix for this:<br>http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&tracker_item_id=28690', 3, 0, 10, '2012-06-19 02:12:05', '2012-07-01 11:00:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/247.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
