(333, 333, NULL, 3, 'Fixed modules modChrome_html5 coding style. Added support not to use "span" at all', 'I fixed coding style of modules.php file as discussed here https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/GyZf9_LgDDU<br><br>Also implemented not to use "Bootstrap size" parameter at all, because adding "spanX" to a class sometimes spoils the output: https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/WACu4ymBd5o', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-27 11:18:26', '2012-10-01 12:20:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/333.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
