(389, 389, NULL, 3, 'Joomla update Purge button', 'If - for some reason - the update feed/stream have been unavailable at least once, the stream is marked as disabled.<br><br>If this happens to any 2.5/3.0 sites, it will require a push on "Purge" under extension updates.<br>Not very intuitive when joomla updates is separated out.<br><br>This is a purge button which resets last check time and enables site update stream again.<br><br>http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&tracker_item_id=29162', 3, 0, 10, '2012-09-15 19:27:22', '2012-09-22 22:59:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/389.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
