(433, 433, 29211, 3, '[#29211] Isis: Jumping table rows on mouseover', 'Navigate e.g. to Extensions -> Module Manager and hover over the title column in different rows. Next to the title, a dropdown toggler is displayed which causes the table row to "jump", meaning that it changes its height.<br><br>http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&tracker_item_id=29211', 3, 0, 10, '2012-09-22 19:34:27', '2012-09-22 19:41:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
