(3197569, 35, 'realityking', 'Closing since this has been committed.', '2011-12-18 23:06:30'),
(3197593, 30, 'realityking', 'A suggestions for the future: Could we please only merge big pull requests like this after they''ve been rebased into just a couple of commits (the less the better, but at least one per author is required). This would make the commit history much more meaningful and easier to read.\r<br>\r<br>It''s really not needed to follow how a feature grew to be, when I browse the history I just wanna see the when the feaute hit the repro.', '2011-12-18 23:10:59'),
(3197612, 45, 'realityking', 'I''d really like to see this one rebased as well. It makes for a much nicer to read history.\r<br>\r<br>Also this contains a platform change, that one should probably first be submitted upstream.', '2011-12-18 23:13:30'),
