(3214013, 42, 'okonomiyaki3000', 'OK, well, I guess this bug will go unreported and unfixed because your tracker site doesn''t work properly. Do you have a tracker for your tracker? Maybe I can report a bug there.', '2011-12-20 03:41:00'),
(3215077, 42, 'elkuku', 'Ah come on, please don''t give up so quickly :)\r<br>The CMS is in a state of "transition". The tracker on joomlacode.org is somewhat "old" and is going to be replaced soon - At least that is what they are saying... We are all waiting eagerly to fill this space here with pull requests because it seems that there are a lot of people getting very comfort with git and GitHub.\r<br>BTW: The code enhancements you are proposing for CodeMirror are looking quite good :) I would recommend though not to mix "topics". This allows for easier testing and further merging of your code.\r<br>\r<br>Keep going, pls ;)', '2011-12-20 06:12:48'),
(3215136, 42, 'okonomiyaki3000', 'It''s no problem. I can wait until joomlacode.org gets updated if that''s what''s required. I have several other enhancements to various parts of the system as well. I''m a big fan of Joomla and I hope to help make it even better. ', '2011-12-20 06:21:37'),
