(3230450, 45, 'infograf768', 'Missing taking of ''true'' line 371 of\r<br>JROOT/components/com_finder/helpers/html/filter.php\r<br>\r<br>should be:\r<br>$html .= JHtml::_(''select.genericlist'', $nodes, ''t[]'', ''class="inputbox"'', ''id'', ''title'', $active, ''tax-'' . JFilterOutput::stringUrlSafe($bv->title));\r<br>\r<br>In the same file change line 369 to\r<br>$html .= JText::sprintf(''COM_FINDER_FILTER_BRANCH_LABEL'', JText::_(''COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_''.$bv->title));\r<br>\r<br>to be able to use the strings:\r<br>COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_AUTHOR="author"\r<br>COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_CATEGORY="category"\r<br>COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_COUNTRY="country"\r<br>COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_EVENT="event"\r<br>COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_ISSUE="issue"\r<br>COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_LABEL="label"\r<br>COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_REGION="region"\r<br>COM_FINDER_QUERY_FILTER_BRANCH_TYPE="type"\r<br>etc.\r<br>\r<br>I still can''t get autocompletion here.\r<br>', '2011-12-21 07:06:16'),
