(3861008, 122, 'elkuku', 'I can imagine the possibility to migrate the database from one engine to another. So the code would be used to check and setup the database for the new engine.\r<br>As a side effect the classes will be picked up by the autoloader.\r<br>Oh, and they fit in the concept that I am trying here:\r<br>https://github.com/elkuku/joomla-cms/tree/multidb/libraries/cms/database\r<br>missing packages for updater, driver and query, which may or not be part of the libraries/joomla package..', '2012-02-08 01:50:33'),
