(7040906, 280, 'phproberto', 'The IE issue was a valuable information to share. That wasn''t here or in joomlacode :(<br><br>Do you have a link with the issue reported with IE?<br><br>I have tested it on Joomla 3.0 + IE8 ( http://i50.tinypic.com/2zhnuo7.png ). Actually I haven''t a VM with IE7. Can you test it?<br><br>Tested: <br>* tabs skip disabled selects<br>* selects remain unclickable<br>* selects keep overlayed<br><br>I have no problem to submit it to platform after fully testing.', '2012-07-17 16:35:30'),
