(7543650, 206, 'mahagr', 'What is the status of this pull request? I really think that Joomla! 3.0 should start moving towards the new platform interfaces, even if it was just an option for the 3rd party components.', '2012-08-07 04:37:48'),
(7545817, 301, 'infograf768', 'Can''t apply patch with eclipse on master for 2 files:<br>components/com_newsfeeds/views/newsfeed/view.html.php<br>and<br>modules/mod_feed/tmpl/default.php', '2012-08-07 07:31:51'),
(7593298, 304, 'Radek-Suski', 'I modified also to allow including an escaped double quotes inside the value (right-hand)<br>Jean Marie asked also for escaped single quotes but as I can see it was always allowed so I think it is not necessary.<br>Beside the AFAIR, there is no need for escaping single quotes inside double quotes.<br>', '2012-08-08 18:48:09'),
(7596819, 304, 'realityking', 'This is awesome!<br><br>Two things, you added some unneeded indentation could you please fix this? Also could you submit this at the platform (https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform/) it will than tickle down with the next merge.<br><br>Thanks again, I was banging my head against the desk for this one but I just don''t speak regex.', '2012-08-08 20:46:15'),
(7606125, 304, 'infograf768', 'Thanks. Works fine.<br>', '2012-08-09 06:11:19'),
