(7926759, 316, 'infograf768', 'icon-bookmark looks good for featured<br>http://s19.postimage.org/n5sy9mfbn/Screen_Shot_2012_08_22_at_09_16_48.png<br><br>pin may be too thin, here in gold, but IMHO, it is the icon which best describe the function<br><br>http://s19.postimage.org/rsz0be2oj/pin.png<br><br>maybe flag is also too thin<br>http://s19.postimage.org/edbzlxu6r/flag.png<br><br>Suggestion: normalize Pinned Banners to use the same icon as Featured.<br><br>We should keep the star for Default, as this has always been used for that purpose.<br><br>', '2012-08-22 07:36:30'),
