(7927680, 316, 'simbus82', 'Joomla! for "featured/home page/default" uses a star from ages, i think we should keep using it...', '2012-08-22 08:26:55'),
(7931708, 316, 'pjwiseman', 'I think they would all be ok especially given the presence of the descriptive button above.<br><br>The "pinned" might be better used for articles pinned to the top of a blog.  I like the clean look of the bookmark, but I think the flag is a better context.<br><br>Is there any major reason to avoid the star?  We have the Home Menu, Default Templates and Featured Articles which are all different contexts so can''t readily be confused.', '2012-08-22 11:49:49'),
