(7944728, 316, 'kyleledbetter', 'I think it makes sense to keep the (gold colored) icon-star for default. For featured, icon-pin seems to make the most sense to me. Maybe we keep the gold color for the star and we can use purple or some other color for the featured pin. Thanks for thinking through this everyone, good discussion', '2012-08-22 18:44:10'),
