(7971869, 320, 'infograf768', 'We have not committed any changes to the installation ini files, except for en-AU and en-US, which are basically the same as en-GB.<br>The other languages will be done when language freeze is declared and call to Translation Teams will be made to get those who commit to produce a 3.0 pack to update their installation ini. Other inis will be deleted from 3.0 (Translation Policy)<br>FYI, Lithuanian language situation in general is now discussed. You may contact me personally by mail about that.', '2012-08-23 14:44:17'),
