(7984414, 166, 'gpongelli', 'Hi Joao,\r<br>actually I''m working on porting this driver to 3.0 , could you test if this\r<br>error is present with this zip ?\r<br>https://github.com/gpongelli/joomla-cms/zipball/postgresql_3.0\r<br>\r<br>Actually I haven''t a 2.5 installation so I can''t replicate nor debug this\r<br>error.\r<br>\r<br>Thank you,\r<br>Eng. Gabriele Pongelli.\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>2012/8/4 Gabriele Pongelli <gabriele.pongelli@gmail.com>\r<br>\r<br>> Thank you for your reporting, I''ll try to solve this error when I''ll come\r<br>> back from holidays.\r<br>> That version is a little bit old, it''s in plan to update 2.5 and realize\r<br>> 3.0 branch with Postgresql fully supported by CMS.\r<br>>\r<br>> Eng. Gabriele Pongelli\r<br>>\r<br>> AVVERTENZE AI SENSI DEL D.LGS. 196/2003\r<br>> Le informazioni contenute in questo messaggio di posta elettronica e negli\r<br>> eventuali files allegati, sono da considerarsi strettamente riservati. Il\r<br>> loro utilizzo è consentito esclusivamente al destinatario del messaggio,\r<br>> per le finalità indicate nel messaggio stesso. Qualora riceveste per errore\r<br>> questo messaggio, Vi preghiamo cortesemente di darcene notizia\r<br>> all''indirizzo e-mail di cui sopra e di procedere alla distruzione del\r<br>> messaggio stesso, cancellandolo dal Vostro sistema; costituisce\r<br>> comportamento contrario ai principi dettati dal D.lgs. 196/2003 il\r<br>> trattenere il messaggio stesso, divulgarlo anche in parte, distribuirlo ad\r<br>> altri soggetti, copiarlo, od utilizzarlo per finalità diverse.\r<br>> This electronic transmission is strictly confidential and intended solely\r<br>> for the addresses. It may contain information which is covered by legal,\r<br>> professional or other privilege. If you are not the intended addressee, you\r<br>> must not disclose, copy or take any action in reliance of this\r<br>> transmission. If you have received this transmission in error, please\r<br>> notify us and delete the received data as soon as possible.\r<br>>\r<br>> Il giorno 03/ago/2012, alle ore 12:50, JoaoSRaposo<\r<br>> reply@reply.github.com>\r<br>> ha scritto:\r<br>>\r<br>> > Hi,\r<br>> >\r<br>> > I''m using your version for about two months and only recently found a\r<br>> bug :)\r<br>> >\r<br>> > When I try to process multiple articles, for example when copying\r<br>> multiple articles from one category to another changing their language, I\r<br>> receive the following error (translated from portuguese):\r<br>> >\r<br>> > The batch process failed with the following message: Failed to archive\r<br>> JTableAsset :: <br /> JLIB_DATABASE_QUERY_FAILED ERROR: null value in the\r<br>> "rules" violates the constraint not null SQL = INSERT INTO "minonl_assets"\r<br>> ("name", "title" , "parent_id", "level", "lft", "RGT") VALUES\r<br>> (''com_content.article.98'', ''Software and Human Resources Management in the\r<br>> Cloud'', 207,4,323,324) RETURNING id\r<br>> >\r<br>> > The result of this operation, is that only one article is copied and\r<br>> mantains de original language.\r<br>> >\r<br>> > In the screencast bellow you can see it happening.\r<br>> >\r<br>> > http://screencast.com/t/31QjGSCiOrxL\r<br>> >\r<br>> > It''s not a serious error so I can continue working with no problem, I\r<br>> just want to let you now ;)\r<br>> >\r<br>> > Regards,\r<br>> >\r<br>> > ---\r<br>> > Reply to this email directly or view it on GitHub:\r<br>> > https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/166#issuecomment-7479773\r<br>>', '2012-08-23 21:17:46'),
