(8597580, 401, 'jneubauer', 'what''s the "standard" for using the badge for denoting hits and/or items?<br>some views have them pushed over to the right using the pull-right class - some have them close to the text like the weblinks category view.<br><br>I was looking at the weblinks category - seems that the subcategories should use the badge for denoting number of links to keep it in sync with other views - but if I send that to the right, it goes all the way over as opposed to the items above that are next to the title.<br><br>I think though that if we''re going to start using the badge - we should use that across the board instead of the old # of links text', '2012-09-16 18:45:15'),
